snippet.title: 20,000 Leagues Under The Sea - Walkabout Mini Golf - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a grand adventure to the depths of the ocean with Walkabout Mini Golf: 20,000 Leagues Under The Sea—the first in a trilogy inspired by Jules Vernes literary masterpieces!

Coming September 29th on @MetaQuestVR and Steam VR
